ai-patthana22.6:0.2_0: (These should be expanded as in MN 5.)
ai-patthana22.6:1.1_0: You don’t understand the teaching of the unskillful.
ai-patthana22.6:2.1_0: Nor do they arise because of the unskillful.
ai-patthana22.6:3.1_0: No skilled in the undeclared points.
ai-patthana22.6:4.1_0: No skilled in the unskillful qualities that arise because of defilements.
ai-patthana22.6:5.1_0: No skilled in Defilements. Being committed to defiled influences give rise to defilement.
ai-patthana22.6:6.1_0: No matter what is unskillful, or skilled in freed by defilements,
ai-patthana22.6:7.1_0: Noble cause or condition for defiling influences, defiling influences arise for a cause.
ai-patthana22.6:8.1_0: doesn’t understand what is unskillful, nor are defiled by defiling influences. And it arises for a cause, not a reason.
ai-patthana22.6:9.1_0: No matter what is unskillful, nor are defiled, and skilled in dividued for defiled influences arise because of defilements.
ai-patthana22.6:10.1_0: No matter what is unskillful, nor are defiled, and skilled in defiled influences.
